Name: SBCBenefitCategoryCS
Title: SBC Benefit Category Code System
Description: Code system for the 30 benefit service rows required in Summary of Benefits and Coverage (SBC) documents per ACA Section 2715 regulations

Name: SBCPlanTypeCS
Title: SBC Plan Type Code System
Description: Code system for health insurance plan types displayed in Summary of Benefits and Coverage documents

Name: PublicationStatus
Title: PublicationStatus
Description: The lifecycle status of an artifact.

Name: BenefitCostApplicability
Title: Benefit cost applicability
Description: Whether the cost applies to in-network or out-of-network providers.

Name: ContactEntityType
Title: Contact entity type
Description: This example value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the purpose for which you would contact a contact party.

Name: InsurancePlanType
Title: Insurance plan type
Description: This example value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate a type of insurance plan.
